    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎各位中国武士们加入下方图片的qq群，与我们一起讨论属于你们的生死故事！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/ee4e8c37acfc725525897605c9cc187c.avif?t=1772216366\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/fbd1847c1fa42712cbe245d3ac8102a0.avif?t=1772216366\" width=590 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/d453da7a789c6a693b582eefddf82443.avif?t=1772216366\" width=590 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>背景设定</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公元1568年，日本——织田信长大军挥师进攻京都，血流成河，战国时代自此拉开帷幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武士、僧兵、浪人与百姓被卷入这场残酷风暴，别无选择，只能拿起兵刃，在战火中求生。每一场战斗，都是你死我活的搏杀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这血腥与杀戮之中，死神——掌管终焉的神祇，看见了人间的杀意已然无需神明干预。男男女女挥舞刀刃，行使死亡的最终裁决。但唯有少数之人，真正成为“屠戮”的化身，他们的复仇之愿，连地狱都无法泯灭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于是，“死神之战”诞生了——那些死后仍渴望继续杀戮的灵魂被重新唤回。他们获得最后一次机会：在杀戮的竞技中夺得胜利，重返人间，继续血的征程，成为死神之选的“终极冠军”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到《二击必杀》！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/af983f4e0c0f63e27be0de40fd58be13.avif?t=1772216366\" width=590 height=159 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/63c4f022f3264abf218576ba92be68ab.avif?t=1772216366\" width=590 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>游戏特色</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受生死一瞬的极致对决！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入《二击必杀》的世界，一场轻量却凶险的2D格斗传奇正等你展开。精美的手绘动画，将你带回日本腥风血雨的乱世。每一刀挥下，皆可能定生死、决胜负。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/eac952eb145335b8c2a43bc9e28ec18c.poster.avif?t=1772216366\" width=590 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/eac952eb145335b8c2a43bc9e28ec18c.webm?t=1772216366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/eac952eb145335b8c2a43bc9e28ec18c.mp4?t=1772216366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现已登场！与八位风格迥异的战士并肩作战，在刀锋交错间书写你的生死传说！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位角色皆拥有独特的战斗技艺与背景，为每一场决斗注入更多变数与战术深度。选择你的武者，踏上通往死神冠军的血路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/169926fbc52c9e9e37a1d1376fb89507.avif?t=1772216366\" width=590 height=470 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >步步为营，每一次出招都可能是你的最后一击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >闪转腾挪，或逼近敌人、或避其锋芒，只为在兵刃相交之际抢占先机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >果断出击是通往胜利之道，但须警惕——套路一旦被识破，便难逃反制之命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以疾行掩其锋芒，虚招试探、乱敌心志，方可制敌于未动之时。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >待胜机显现之刻，便以雷霆一击终结战局，夺回属于你的荣耀！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/acc0b211408742438b67beab6c96c486.poster.avif?t=1772216366\" width=590 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/acc0b211408742438b67beab6c96c486.webm?t=1772216366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586750/extras/acc0b211408742438b67beab6c96c486.mp4?t=1772216366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
